Terry

27
00:02:27,213 --> 00:02:29,875
Where is Candy?

28
00:02:29,949 --> 00:02:32,247
We are looking for her as well

29
00:02:32,318 --> 00:02:34,582
She didn't come to the banquet

30
00:02:35,955 --> 00:02:37,855
