52
00:03:43,556 --> 00:03:47,083
Is that someone alright?
the person you are going to see

53
00:03:49,095 --> 00:03:50,687
No problem.

54
00:03:50,763 --> 00:03:53,061
My cart is the fastest in Chicago.

55
00:04:08,448 --> 00:04:10,507
Here we are.

56
00:04:12,485 --> 00:04:15,113
